软件介绍：

欢迎使用北京大学自行车协会论坛（CAPUBBS）iOS客户端

CAPUBBS iOS客户端包含功能：
-登录、注册、查看、修改、切换账户
-发表、查看、回复、编辑、删除帖子和楼中楼
-查看系统消息和私信消息
-查看论坛热点、在线用户、签到统计
-搜索、收藏论坛帖子
-分享内容到微信、QQ、微博等
-举报违规帖子/用户/私信

祝使用愉快！欢迎反馈意见和建议！

审核信息：

Users must agree to the End User License Agreement (EULA) before using the app. The EULA is presented when the app is first launched, and users cannot proceed without accepting it. The EULA clearly states a zero-tolerance policy for objectionable or abusive content, and describes how such content will be handled.
若要使用本软件，用户必须在首次启动时同意用户协议（EULA）。若拒绝协议，则无法继续使用软件。EULA 明确声明对违规、骚扰或不当内容采取零容忍政策，并说明处理机制。

Registration is not required to use the app. Unregistered users can browse most content (except for the working board) and use features such as search. When registering, users are not required to provide private information such as gender—they may leave it blank or choose “Confidential.”
本软件不强制注册。未注册用户可浏览除工作区外的大部分内容，并可正常使用搜索等功能。注册时不强制填写隐私信息，如性别字段可留空或选择“保密”。

Our servers automatically scan all user-generated content for potentially inappropriate material. If potential violations are detected, the content will not be publicly visible until it has been reviewed and approved by our moderators.
我们的服务器会自动扫描用户发布的内容，若发现潜在违规内容，将在审核通过后才予以公开展示。

Users can report posts, users, or private messages they believe to be inappropriate. To report a post, find report button in the action button under bottom bar. To report a user, find report button in their user info page. Our moderation team handles all reports within 24 hours. Verified violations may result in content deletion, account suspension, or permanent bans. Users may be notified of the results via private message.
用户可举报认为违规的帖子、用户或私信。举报帖子时，点击底部操作栏中的“更多”按钮，找到举报选项；举报用户时，在其用户信息页面中找到“举报用户”按钮。我们团队会在24小时内处理所有举报，经核实后可删除内容、封禁账号或永久移除用户，并可通过私信通知处理结果。

Users can request to delete their account within the app, by scrolling to the bottom of the user info page. Once confirmed, all user-related data will be permanently removed from our database.
用户可在 App 内用户信息页面底部申请删除账号。确认后，与用户相关的所有数据将永久删除，无法恢复。

